imdb.plot outline: Join us every Thursday night on Fox Sports North and Fox Sports Wisconsin as we celebrate the outdoor lifestyle in the upper Midwest. Hosted by Bill Sherck and Laura Schara, Due North Outdoors shares stories and adventures from life in the outdoors. Hunting, Fishing, Camping and so much more. Now in it's 10th year of production, we seek to find unique people, places and pursuits and bring them to you.
imdb.title: Due North Outdoors
